{"tid":720580,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟巴士上層嘅孖位係咪比兩個人坐?","createTime":"2018-06-28T04:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T03:13:53.000Z","uid":6539,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a380f2833213d61530a0b26b7091cc3ed8b45065","tid":720580,"uid":6539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"一程巴士真係可以睇盡人生百態<br />\n我明白長途巴士大家都想坐得舒服啲<br />\n但我一上到上層 竟然一個位都無<br />\n唔係因為架巴士好爆好多人坐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係 因 為 比 啲 袋 坐 撚 曬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/121301_c56e16720f78335b139e17447de9a9f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F121301_c56e16720f78335b139e17447de9a9f4.png&h=ad4295ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於是我死死地行到去最後嗰行<br />\n結果 我都只係可以坐中間<br />\n因為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">電 話 都 可 以 坐 一 個 位 ！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/122021_39913fe7ebbfe4bc890cfcecc166dad1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F122021_39913fe7ebbfe4bc890cfcecc166dad1.png&h=b4d69b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廢老就好啦 兩蚊雞兩個位 好撚抵搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 究竟可以幾自私?"},{"pid":"97ef6729ed725687750acdbc13e4da941971c1c3","tid":720580,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"一嘢就落去啦"},{"pid":"489d06170db7fa2d41eaf133b2988b95dff7c04f","tid":720580,"uid":91720,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"a380f2833213d61530a0b26b7091cc3ed8b45065","tid":720580,"uid":6539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"一程巴士真係可以睇盡人生百態<br />\n我明白長途巴士大家都想坐得舒服啲<br />\n但我一上到上層 竟然一個位都無<br />\n唔係因為架巴士好爆好多人坐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"colo